parameters.text:
=You are a viral content strategist for LinkedIn.

Using the details below, create a structured LinkedIn post outline with 5 sections:
1. Hook
2. Problem
3. Value or Lesson
4. Solution or Takeaway
5. Call-to-action (CTA)

Topic: {{ $json.output.topic }}
Industry: {{ $json.output.niche }}
Tone: {{ $json.output.tone }}
Key Points: {{ $json.output.key_points }}

parameters.jsonSchemaExample:
{
  "structure": {
    "hook": "🚀 How a Shopify store owner saved 12 hours/week by automating replies",
    "problem": "Manual replies were taking hours daily.",
    "value": "AI automation now handles 90% of questions instantly.",
    "solution": "Connected Shopify inbox with AI-driven autoresponder.",
    "cta": "Want to save your time too? Comment 'AUTOMATE' below 💬"
  }
}
